  "title": "Tax Senior",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company: Cypress Singapore PAC</strong></p>\n<p>Cypress Policy of Trust &amp; Empowerment allows flexible working arrangements that allow lifestyle choices and managing childcare or eldercare needs. Workloads will be allocated taking into consideration each candidate’s situation<strong>. </strong>Cypress adopts a one-on-one mentoring program with junior staff to guide and enrich them with work-related training.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Title: Tax Senior</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide high quality and professional tax compliance services to a portfolio of international clients and SMEs in diverse range of industries</li>\n  <li>Prepare clients' corporate tax returns and submissions</li>\n  <li>Assist clients in responding to queries from the tax authorities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Position Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Member of Singapore Chartered Tax Professionals preferred</li>\n  <li>Bachelor of Finance/Accounting, Professional Qualification or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in a professional tax practice</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills, able to work well with employees at all levels</li>\n</ul>",
